y":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T17:39:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>緊係喊啦...點知金仔想點整我...原來虛驚一場</blockquote><br />\n你就想，一陣爬完攞籌排隊等打「吧」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">唔識打個字</span></blockquote><br />\n靶喎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n原來我打錯碼，怪唔知得一路打唔到個字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10f112c3847f5e9e30b32d43f226063901715038","tid":170262,"uid":96323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T17:40:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a07c0355cd3a3f7c6717deea87f23101bd82292","tid":170262,"uid":3117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T17:45:29.000Z","msg":"好快犬決"},{"pid":"8bb44da6a4ee7105ab8aa78c82f474fb24e9c3b1","tid":170262,"uid":66951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T17:49:03.000Z","msg":"北韓佬起碼都係焗住喊<br />\n班黃絲係真心膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n結論：北韓佬》黃絲"},{"pid":"3dcd6476f2ba92de6c1e39c46e3b1c117447718d","tid":170262,"uid":64609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T17:56:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>金正恩竟然比軍官爬佢背<br />\n比佢老豆好<br />\n係lesser evil</blockquote><br />\n笑撚左 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}